                     <interp inst="t18460921-1940-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 1 box, value 1<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; and llb. weight of cheroots, 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18460921-name-963" type="victimName">
